    • Constructor Detail

      • Roof

        public Roof(boolean isHighRoof,
            RoofMaterials roofmaterial,
            double carportLength,
            double carportWidth)
        The constructor for roof calls calculation methods from the class CalcRoofMaterials. I use these to determine the values for roof - The global variabels are set upon creating a instance of roof.
        Parameters:
        isHighRoof: - Boolean value to show if the roof is high or flat
        roofmaterial: - Material of the roof
        carportLength: - Length of the carport, roof length is determined upon this value
        carportWidth: - Width of the carport, roof width is determined upon this value.
